lead_paragraph: Bill and Hillary Clinton teamed up with Arizona Sen. John McCain at the start of an annual meeting of college students on Friday, putting on stage a former president, a onetime Republican presidential nominee and perhaps a future White House candidate.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Urges Students to Participate
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Urges Students to Participate
